name: Planet Strike
description:
Humanity struggle to survive after a global cataclysm has caused by an extinction event. There is only one planet found suitable for us to live in. It is called "Epsilon Eridani". But the destination is so faraway. There are 55 planets to be jumped over. 

GOOD LUCK!! 

Can humanity survive?

It is up to you...

------------------------

Be careful not to crash on asteroids.

One tap to send spaceships.

Let us what you think afterwards.
